text: East Union is an unincorporated community in Hamilton and Tipton counties, in the U.S. state of Indiana. The community is part of the Kokomo, Indiana, Metropolitan Statistical Area. ==Geography== East Union is located at . ==References== Category:Unincorporated communities in Tipton County, Indiana Category:Unincorporated communities in Indiana Category:Kokomo, Indiana metropolitan area
